item.title: About
item.description: I am a Doctor of Veterinary medicine licensed in Croatia and Switzerland. Currently on career leave to raise a family. Work history Volounteer work at the VEF clinics for internal medicine (2012. - 2014.) Volounteer work at the Khulula Wildlife Center, South Africa (2013.) Volounteer work at the county veterinary station in Varaždin (2005.) Teaching TA on the Internal Medicine classes (2013. - 2014.) TA on the Comparative Anatomy 101, 102, 103 classes (2009.
